    rating: "Very Bad"
    comments: "The dialogue is very bad and cringey, it is as if AI wrote this movie; the humor is forced and does not hit most of the time; the symbolism is not focused because they try to make this movie an allergory for the current presidential regime, but they give up on this halfway through the movie; the movie also tries to introduce character doubt, but they give up on this also; the foreshadowing is bad because they just force plot points as you just have to expect things are going to happen because of the current track record of Marvel"
